Package jrobo.expectusafterlun.ch

Class MircColors

java.lang.Object
jrobo.expectusafterlun.ch.MircColors
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListColors
public class MircColors extends Object
This class will define constants and methods for sending colors to channels That have /mode +c allowed in the channel Color codes http://www.weechat.org/files/doc/stable/weechat_user.en.html#command_line_colors
